inn1.comm: starts off with a good one outside the off stump, in the corridor, watches it closely and lets it go.
terrible delivery down the leg side, Mushfiqur Rahim had no chance to get to it and down to the fence.
good length delivery swinging away outside the off stump, left alone.
good length delivery in line with the off stump, defends with the full face off the bat down the track.
defends with an open face to backward point.
a straight delivery this time from Mortaza outside the off stump, left alone through to Mushfiqur Rahim.
good ball to end the first over, was on target, defended to the off side to point.
moves forward and drives well to mid-off.
nicely played and well fielded, moves forward in line and works to the fielder at short midwicket.
few steps down the track and clips it in the air to deep-square leg.
it was full and wide outside the off stump, How goes after it and gets an outside edge in the air down to thirdman, lucky the ball did not carry to that fielder.
works it to the fielder at short midwicket.
pitched up delivery driven back to Shahadat Hossain, who shows some aggression by throwing the ball back past the batsman to the keeper.
gets behind the delivery and defends to the off side, bowling at 130 km/h.
defends with a straight bat down the track.
works it through midwicket, puts pressure on the fielder, was a chance for run out if the fielder had picked up the ball.
inside edge onto the pads and then to the on side.
good length delivery on target, defended to the off side.
walks a few steps down the track and defends to cover.
pitched up delivery driven to mid-off.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, gets behind it and defends to cover.
moves forward in line and pushes to cover.
fuller and wide outside the off stump, unable to find the gap, plays it to the fielder at cover.
adavances forward and looking to go for the big shot, Shahadat Hossain does well to put it short of a length forcing the batsman to defend.
emphatic shot in the gap between extra-cover and mid-off to the fence. The ball races through the quick outfield.

worked square behind the wicket, coming back quickly for the second run, Tushar Imran picks up the ball and scores a direct hit, referred to the third umpire. Not out comes up on the screen. McCullum makes it in.
short of a length delivery defended.
short ball pulled in the air and on the bounce to the fielder at deep-square leg.
defended with the full face off the bat to the off side.
good shot, moves forward and cuts on the front foot square of the wicket to point boundary.
punches off the back foot to the fielder at cover.
steps down the track and whips it in the air to fine leg fence.
pushes to mid-on, Ashraful unnecessarily throws down the stumps at the strikers end.
moves forward in line and defends with the full face off the bat to the off side.
loud shout for lbw turned down as the ball was sliding down the leg side.
another appeal turned down, again McCullum down the track and looking to work it to the onside, off the pad the ball goes to the off side.
pitched up delivery and what does McCullum do, he launches it over the long off fence for maximum, good strike.
there was some noise as the edge was taken by Mushfiqur Rahim, loud appeal for a caught-behind turned down. looked out for sure but umpire Parker shakes his head.
cracking shot, moves forward and drives well through covers to the fence.
short of a length delivery defended to the off side.
worked to the onside for a single.
moves forward and punches wide of mid-off for a quick single.
goes for the pull and misses, through to Mushfiqur Rahim.
on the middle and leg, worked to the right of deep-square leg for couple of runs.
comes down the track, Shahadat Hossain watches it and pitches it short, McCullum was not in a position to play any shot, lets it go through to Mushfiqur Rahim.
Shahadat Hossain was lucky as the ball was played to the short fine leg, the fielder does well to prevent a certain boundary.
left alone outside the off stump.
pitches outside the leg stump and strikes the pad as McCullum goes for a big heave on the onside, loud appeal turned down.
full and on the legs, worked to the right of deep-square leg for couple of runs.
pushes on the front foot to mid-on.
gets behind a short of a length delivery outside the off stump and defends to cover.
once again defends with an angled bat to the off side.
moves forward and punches the ball to the fielder at extra-cover.
moves forward and drives straight to the fielder at mid-off, does not find the gap.
punches it well down the track, unlucky as the ball strikes the stumps at the non-strikers end.
pushes in the gap square of the wicket on the off side front of the wicket for an easy single.
good ball coming in, moves forward and pushes to mid-on.
wonderfully played, few steps down the track and works it nicely to fine leg fence.
slightly short and How goes for the pull, does not time it well, fielder at midwicket does well.
driven on the up and on the bounce to Aftab Ahmed at extra-cover.
there is a fielder in the deep as How drives on the up through covers.
driven to the fielder at cover.
short of a length delivery coming in, cramping for room, forces him to defend to the off side, was looking for a single.
this time bit wide outside the off stump, pushes to Farhad Reza at backward point who has a shy at the stumps, strikes it.
plays in the gap to the left of Reza at backward point to the deep.

few steps down the track and goes after the delivery, he was looking to play to the onside, gets an outside edge past the keeper to the fence, for a moment Mortaza thought it was going into the keeper s gloves.
driven well to the sweeper cover for a single.
moves forward and works to the onside.
good running, plays it in the gap between midwicket and mid-on.
pushes well on the front foot to mid-off for a quick single.
gets the outside edge as McCullum pushes forward goes to thirdman fence.
another boundary, down the track and hits it in the air to long on fence.
repeats the shot, down the track and hits it well in the air to long on fence.
driven nicely to the left of mid-off, poor fielding by Ashraful, who lets it go through him, the ball races along the turf to the fence.
pushes to mid-off, this time Ashraful gets a cheer as he fields the ball.
moves forward and works to the right of mid-on for a single.
defends with the full face off the bat to the off side.
defends to the off side.
down the track and hits it high in the air, goes very high, Tushar Imran running around from deep-backward square leg does well to prevent the ball from going into the fence.
good shot to find the gap. Down the track and hits in the gap between midwicket and mid-on to the fence.
pushes to point and takes off for a quick single, would have been close if the throw was accurate.

RUN OUT!  down the track and cuts to deep-backward point, Tushar Imran swoops on the ball and puts in a good throw to Mushfiqur Rahim, who gets rid of the bails, referred to the third umpire, "OUT" flashes on the screen. McCullum goes for 35.
defended to the off side.
worked to the onside.
another mix-up, as Fulton plays to cover-point and takes off for a single, the throw from Ashraful was bad, it goes way over the keeper, they get an overthrow.
good length delivery outside the off stump, left alone.
defends with a straight bat to the off side.
another good delivery defended to the off side.
pushes to mid-on.
pushes forward and plays to mid-on.
played to the right of mid-on for a quick single.
plays to the right of Farhad Reza and takes off for a single, shy at the stumps misses.
driven hard to the fielder at cover.
moves forward and pushes to mid-on.
down the track and pulls well in the air to midwicket fence, good positive strike from How.
driven to mid-off.
terrible fielding at extra-cover, a full toss outside the off stump, driven well to wide long off fence. How gets to his 50!
sweetly timed, clips it to deep-square leg fence.
defended on the front foot to the off side.
pushed to cover for a single.
driven on the front foot to mid-off.
plays late to backward point.
plays to backward point.
inside edge to fine leg fence.
driven to long on
good ball, How moves across his stumps and looks to work it through the onside, misses it, strikes the pad in line with the stumps, loud shout, given by umpire Tony Hill.
driven to cover.
driven to wide long off for couple of runs.
defended down the track.
driven to long off for a single.
cuts on the front foot to backward point.
pushes to point for a quick single, shy at the stumps misses.
good ball defended on the track.
off the pad to the off side as Styris looks to work it to the onside.
down the track and pushes back to the bowler.
another terrible fielding, Styris cuts to deep-backward point, Tushar makes a mess of it.
cut once again to deep-backward point, this time Tushar in quickly.
pushed to the onside.
moves forward and drives well to the sweeper cover for a single.
slightly short outside the off stump, cut to the left of sweeper cover for another single.
slower through the air, moves forward and pushes to backward point.
moves forward and plays to the left of extra-cover for a single.
moves back and works to the onside.
punches off the back foot to the sweeper cover.
short ball cut to sweeper cover, good running comes back for the second run.
full on the legs, worked through square leg.
driven to long on
driven nicely to deep-extra cover for couple of runs.
works it to the onside, Ashraful at midwicket puts in a dive to stop it, cannot prevent the single.
punches on the front foot to the sweeper cover for a single.
lofts it in the air, placed it nicely to deep-extra cover, comes back easily for the second run.
replay of the same shot, lofts it once again in the air to deep-extra cover.
driven on the front foot down the ground to long off.
punches to extra cover.
not a controlled stroke from Styris, chips it in the air wide of the fielder at cover to the deep.
driven down the ground to long on.
defended to the onside.
driven to mid-on for a single.
moves forward and works it to square leg outside the circle for an easy single.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long on.
waits on the back foot and punches down the ground to long on.
pushes down the track to long on.
driven back to the bowler.
brings up his 50! driven to the sweeper cover and comes back for the second run.
moves back and drives to mid-on, the fielder from midwicket makes a desperate attempt to stop the ball, fails to do so.
driven to the off side.
spins away, Styris cuts and misses.
driven on the front foot to the sweeper cover for an easy single.
tossed up delivery driven to deep-mid on for a single.
waits in the crease and punches to mid-off.
driven down the ground to long on.
waits in the crease and punches down the ground to long on.
punches off the back foot to the sweeper cover.
moves forward and pushes in the gap to point for an easy single.
down the track and plays to cover for a single.
driven to mid-off.
pushes to the off side.
driven to the right of the bowler, who moves across and fields it.
pushes on the front foot to backward point.
wonderful fielding by Aftab, dives to his left and makes a good save, cut hard to the left of backward point.
driven down the ground to long on.
moves forward and works behind square leg.
tossed right up, driven down the ground to long on.
good shot down the ground to the left of long on.
good shot once again, tossed right up outside the off stump, driven to wide long off for couple of runs, brings up the 50 partnership.
driven down the ground to long on.
moves forward and works along the ground straight to the fielder at midwicket.
moves forward and drives well to extra cover, good fielding.
dropped! it was full and hit straight back to Reza, who drops it.
pitched up delivery outside the off stump, driven down the ground to long off, brings up the 200 for New Zealand.
well played, paddles it around to fine leg.
driven to backward point.
chips it in the air to deep-extra cover, comes back for the second run.
waits in the crease and pushes to point, quick call of "NO".
this time he gets the single as he pushes in the gap to cover.
down the leg side, looking to paddle it around, misses it.
driven on the front foot to long off.
good fielding at cover-point, driven on the front foot.
loud appeal for caught-behind from the bowler and keeper, turned down by umpire Hill as Styris looks to play a late cut.
good strike from Fulton, picks it up and launches it high and over long on, Siddique takes the catch outside the ropes.
driven down the ground to long on for couple of runs.
driven down the ground to long off.
keeps it full and wide outside the off stump, mistimes the shot to the off side.
moves slightly across his stumps and takes it on the full and works it to deep-backward square leg.
another low full toss outside the off stump, played straight to the fielder along the ground to backward point.
goes for the sweep and gets a top-edge, Mushfiqur thought that he could get it, but it goes a long way to the fence.
sweeps it in the air to deep-midwicket, Mortaza dives too early for the catch and misses it completely.
defended on the front foot to cover.
uses his feet and cuts to sweeper cover.
driven along the ground straight to the fielder at extra cover.
driven down the ground to long on.
full and wide outside the off stump, goes after it and misses it, good work by Mushfiqur Rahim to collect the ball.
heaves it across straight along the ground to the fielder at midwicket.
good ball in the block-hole, dug out to the off side.
slower delivery from Reza, looking once again to chip it in the air, was too early into the shot, gets the outside edge straight into the hands of Tushar Imran at short thirdman.
full toss driven to the sweeper cover to get off the mark.
driven along the ground to mid-off.
dabs it in the gap on the off side for a single.
driven down the ground to long off.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long on.
moves slightly back and punches down the ground to long off, Tamim Iqbal misfields to allow the second run.
cheeky shot, paddles it around to fine leg.
driven down the ground to long off.
driven hard to extra cover, shy at the stumps misses, would have been close.
pitched up delivery driven to the sweeper cover.
once again hit hard to extra cover, no single this time.
driven back down the track to the bowler and Reza looks to throw down the stumps.
good ball in the block-hole, dug out back to the bowler.
slower delivery and Fulton hits down the ground to long on.
inside edge to the off side.
bad ball down the leg side.
comes down the track and looks it heave it across, mistimes to long on.
waits for the turn on the front foot and works it in front of square leg.
tossed up outside the off stump, goes for a big heave on the onside, gets an edge and Mushfiqur Rahim takes the catch as the ball lobs up off his shoulders.
comes forward and defends to the off side.
yorker length delivery forced to the sweeper cover for a single.
full toss not put away, hit to the fielder at extra-cover.
once again driven straight to the fielder at extra cover along the ground.
full toss hit to the right of backward point, half stopped by the fielder.
full toss driven down the ground to long on.
full and wide outside the off stump, difficult for Mushfiqur Rahim as he standing up.
wide outside the off stump, cuts and misses, hits hard on Mushfiqur Rahim's gloves.
moves slighty across his stumps and works just outside the circle on the onside, comes quickly back for the second run, good running.
works it nicely behi.nd square leg for a single
moves forward and works to midwicket.
worked to square leg for a single.
moves forward and pushes in the gap through cover for a single.
looking for the reverse sweep, misses it and through to Rahim.
yorker length delivery outside the off stump, squeezed out to thirdman for a single.
heaves it across to deep-square leg, a slower delivery, one hand was off the handle as he hit it.
takes it on the full and paddles it around to fine leg for couple of runs.
nicely bowled and well played, pushes to mid-on.
poor fielding, played to cover-point.
stumping missed! Full delivery outside the off stump, Taylor walks down the track and looks to heave to the midwicket fence, misses it and Mushfiqur Rahim fumbles it.
moves back and punches it down the ground to long on.
moves across his stumps and looks to play to the onside, misses it, off the body to the off side.
full toss driven to the sweeper cover.
down the track and works to deep-square leg.
finds the gap this time and strikes it well, picks up outside the off stump and swings it in the air to midwicket fence.
another powerful strike, swings it hard and in the air, one bounce to the midwicket fence.
fuller length delivery driven to long off, ricochets off the stumps they go through for an overthrow.
swings and misses outside the off stump.
it was coming, picks it up nicely and swings it high and over midwicket fence for maximum.
bowls it too wide outside the off stump, Oram lets it go.
clever batting from Oram, moves right across his stumps and tucks it to fine leg, good running.
full delivery driven down the ground to long on.
good powerful strike from Oram, full toss outside the off stump, swings it high and over the long on fence for maximum.
not timed well, pulls it to deep-square leg for a single.
low full toss outside the off stump, squeezed to backward point for a single.
good powerful shot from Taylor, picks up the slower delivery and swings it high and over midwicket fence, brings up the 300 for New Zealand.
yorker squeezed out to the off side.
what a shot! It was a full toss wide outside the off stump, just puts the bat in line and finds the gap past the backward point to the fence.
fuller delivery outside the off stump, driven along the ground straight to the fielder at extra cover.
full and down the leg side, off the pad behind the wicket, appeal turned down as the ball was sliding down.
full delivery, Oram opens up and drives it well in the gap to extra cover fence.
another shot but not perfectly timed but goes all the way over wide long on fence for maximum. Great forearms of Oram.
bouncer, Oram sways away from the line, good aggression.
slower delivery and Oram too early into the shot misses it completely, goes through to Mushfiqur Rahim.
yorker squeezed out to the sweeper cover for a single.
big hit from Oram, picks it up and hits in the air and one bounce to cover fence.
short ball, Oram clears his right leg and looks to pull, misses it.
another short delivery a bouncer, goes way over the head of Oram, signals a wide.
goes all the way, another massive hit from Oram, slower delivery picked up and hit over the long on fence.
50!  for Oram, goes for the big hit, gets a big outside edge, the ball flies down to thirdman fence.
played to deep-backward square leg, comes back for the second run.
full toss and Oram looks to go big and out of the park but does not time it well, goes high in the air, Tamim runs across and takes a good catch at long off.

inn2.comm: nice start, driven nicely on the up through extra covers to the fence.
short rising delivery climbs up on Tamim, who jumps up and defends it to the off side.
another good shot, on the middle and leg, tucked it nicely to square leg fence.
moves back and punches it back to the bowler.
excellent delivery surprises Tamim Iqbal, short rising delivery, jumps up and looks to defend, beats the outside edge.
another excellent short rising delivery, this time he lets it go.
works it off his hips to deep-backward square leg for couple of runs.
good ball angled across, left alone.
moves across his stumps and works it to midwicket.
gets behind a short of a length delivery and defends well to the off side.
off the pad behind the wicket on the onside.
short delivery dug in, jumps up and nudges it behind square leg for a single.
good looking shot from Tamim Iqbal, rocks back and punches to the cover fence.
gets behind it and defends well with a straight bat.
firmly driven to mid-off, straight to Vettori.
another firm shot on the up to mid-off.
up on his toes and works it through midwicket for a single.
sends down a bouncer and Siddiqui ducks under it.
whips it through midwicket to the deep, Fulton chases it and puts in a good slide to pull the ball back in, saves a run.
bouncer, ducks under it.
moves forward in line and drives to mid-off.
poor effort from Gillespie at long leg, it was on the legs worked to the right of the fielder, who lets the ball go through to the fence after making lot of ground to reach it.
good length delivery defended to the off side.
good length delivery defended with straight bat back down the track.
short of a length delivery defended.
goes for the drive and gets beaten, Mills having a few words with the batsman.
defended back down the track.
worked left of mid-on for a single.
digs in a bouncer, ducks under it.
another bouncer which goes harmlessly over the batsman as he ducks under it.
punched to mid-on.
moves forward and drives on the up to the off side, Ross Taylor at short cover picks up the ball and underarms the ball and strikes the stumps at the non-strikers end, the batsman was well in.
defended to the off side.
short delivery outside the off stump, cuts it in the air over backward point to the deep.
short ball pulled straight to the fielder along the ground to square leg.
good shot in the air and in the gap to cover fence. It was a full delivery outside the off stump.
eased away to the off side.
short of a length delivery, tucks it off his hips to deep midwicket for a single.
nice firm drive on the up to mid-off but unable to find the gap.
good length delivery outside the off stump, plays and misses.
moves forward in line and pushes to the onside, Mills moves across and fields the ball.
good bouncer, ducks under it.
short of a length delivery defended to the off side.
fuller delivery driven firmly to mid-off.
plays too early, gets a leading edge but the ball falls safely on the off side.
short delivery, up on his toes and defends to cover.
short delivery worked to the onside.
short rising delivery outside the off stump, up on his toes and plays it behind square leg.
excellent bouncer, it was bit quicker and Tamim Iqbal ducks just in time but leaves  his bat in the air.
on the legs turned to square leg for a single.
down the leg side and off the pads to fine leg fence.
wonderful shot, moves forward in line and drives on the up through extra cover, the ball races along the turf to the fence as Vettori chases in vain.
ducks under the bouncer.
short of a length delivery and Siddique defends on the track.
punches it firmly down the track, Martin half stops on his follow-through.
driven to mid-off, a mix-up, recovers in time.
short delivery outside the off stump, left alone.
nice shot whipped through midwicket to the fence.
short of a length delivery pushed to mid-on for a single.
short delivery, mistimes the pull to short fine leg.
short of a length delivery on the off and middle, defended to the onside.

played to the off side, Junaid Siddique from the non-strikers end takes off for a single, complete mix-up, the throw from the fielder comes in but nobody to take it at the bowlers end. Mills unhappy with the effort from Oram. Run out chance missed.
defended to the off side.
cut hard in the air, just short of Taylor at cover.
good length delivery defended down the track.
steers it down to thirdman for a single.
opens the face off the bat and runs it down to thirdman for an easy single.
moves across his stumps and whips it to deep-square leg.
goes all way, it was full and down the leg side, flicks it in the air and over backward square leg fence.
gets his line wrong again, strays down the leg side, flicks it in the air to backward square leg fence.
worked behind square leg.
what a shot! comes down the track and smashes it past the bowler to the fence.

short delivery and Junaid Siddique looks to go for the pull shot, mishits it high in the air to mid-on, Jeetan Patel the substitute settles under it and takes the catch. Bangladesh lose their first wicket.
aggression from Mills, sends down a bouncer, which is a bit high, not signaled.
defended to the off side.
full outside the off stump, Ashraful nicely in position steers it down to the right of thirdman for a single.
short of a length delivery angled across, looking to work it to the onside, gets a leading edge, the ball lands safely on the off side.
second wicket goes down. It was angled across and Tamim Iqbal looking to glide it down to the thirdman, gets the outside edge to McCullum behind the wicket.
pulls a short delivery, gets a top-edge, the ball flies over the keeper and falls safely.
sends down a bouncer, which goes over the batsman, signaled wide.
moves forward to a good length delivery and defends to the onside.
short delivery outside the off stump, left alone through to McCullum.
another short delivery outside the off stump, lets it go.
good length delivery on target, defends with the full face of the bat back down the track.
wide outside the off stump, left alone.
fuller delivery outside the off stump, driven nicely but straight to the fielder along the ground to mid-off.
left alone outside the off stump.
good shot but cannot find the gap, hit hard to the cover fielder.
short delivery outside the off stump, Ashraful goes for a pull shot and misses.
short outside the off stump, left alone.
pitched up delivery driven in the air, did it carry to Taylor at cover? The players appeal for a catch, the umpires discuss and they go up to the third umpire. Given and Ashraful has to go.
defended on the front foot.
left alone outside the off stump.
short delivery outside the off stump, moves across and plays inside the line and lets the ball go.
bouncer, ducks under it.
moves forward and pushes to mid-off.
short delivery outside the off stump, up on his toes and defends to the off side.
good length delivery on target, defended back to the bowler.
back of a length delivery coming into the batsman, defended to the off side.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, left alone.
another good delivery defended back to the bowler.
sends down a bouncer, which goes high and down the leg side, signaled wide.
short delivery outside the off stump, left alone.
short of a length delivery defended to the onside.
comes forward and defends beside the track.
moves forward to the pitch off the delivery and drives wide of long off.
moves forward and pushes to point.
turn and bounce as Tushar Imran plays forward, gets beaten.
played to the off side.
lovely flighted delivery outside the off stump, which goes straight on, left alone.
gets behind the short of a length delivery and defends with a straight bat to the off side.
pushes to mid-on.
short ball pulled to deep-square leg.
inside edges onto the pads.
beautiful shot, it was short and wide outside the off stump, rolls his wrist and cuts well past backward point to the fence.
feels for the delivery outside the off stump and gets beaten.
plays it back down the track.
a premeditated sweep shot, gets beaten.
pushed to long on for a single.
a touch short, cuts and misses.
loud appeal as the ball strikes high on the pad, turned down.
pushed to mid-on.
moves in line and pushes to mid-on.
back of a length delivery, dabs it to the onside for a quick single.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, defended to the off side.
played to the onside for a quick single as Oram runs across and picks up the ball and has a shy at the stumps, misses it.
a slow bouncer, surprises Aftab, who lets it go and then looks at the umpire for a signal.
defended on the back foot down the track.
nicely tossed up delivery, comes forward and defends on the track.
bit quicker from Vettori, works to the onside.
a touch short, moves back and plays down the track.
cuts late to backward point, Jeetan Patel does well.
slower through the air, defends to the off side.
moves back and works to short fine leg, a very good over from Vettori comes to an end.
gets behind a short of a length delivery and plays to backward point.
short delivery coming into the batsman, who looks to make room and cut, misses it and through to McCullum.
a great effort by Vettori to take the catch as Aftab hits high in the air to midwicket outside the circle, had to run a long way and across, just gets an hand to it.
slower delivery, gets the outside edge and falls just in front of McCullum.
turned to square leg for a single.
worked to square leg.
played to deep-backward square leg
good sweep shot, plays it behind square leg in the gap to the fence.
arm ball defended to the onside.
moves forward but plays down the wrong line as the ball strikes the pad.
moves forward and drives it down the track.
turns it around behind square leg.
on the middle and leg, nudged to fine leg.
punches on the front foot to the sweeper cover for couple of runs.
good length delivery on target, pushes to mid-on for a single.
moves in line and turns it around to square leg.
defended to the off side.
down the track and gave himself some room, slashes it in the air to deep cover.
played down to thirdman.
loud shout for lbw, struck in line but bit high, turned down.
comes forward and defends to the off side.
arm ball cut to the sweeper cover for a single.
a touch short, waits in the crease and defends to the off side.
comes forward and defends.
pushes to mid-on for a single.
nicely turned away to deep-square leg.
plays with an angled bat to the off side.
wonderful timing on the shot. It was short and wide outside the off stump, got on top of it nicely and cuts it behind point to the fence.
short ball pulled well past the square leg fielder to the fence, rocks nicely on the back foot.
short of a length delivery on target, gets behind it and defends to the off side.
moves forward and drives well down the ground to long off.
